      <title>泰铢汇率因央行自主权担忧而落后于其他货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/baht-lags-behind-peers-on-concerns-over-central-bank-autonomy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心泰国央行的独立性进一步受到削弱，泰国货币在亚洲其他货币中跌幅最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/baht-lags-behind-peers-on-concerns-over-central-bank-autonomy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 04:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
